title: Ep171 Forensic Entomology
description: This week, the gals bug out over some creepy-crawly crimes and criminals. Topics include the dining preferences of blow flies, exonerating eggs, and a parking lot of horrors. Pour a nice big glass of Winc's Field Theory Cabernet Pfeffer, double check your salad, and tune in for Forensic Entomology. For a full list of show sponsors, visit www.wineandcrimepodcast.com/support
